{
  "title": "Dark Smoked Kenyan Lamb Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful Kenyan dish featuring lamb, molasses, and smoked spices, perfect for a weeknight dinner. This stew is also anti-inflammatory friendly due to the presence of turmeric and ginger.",
  "cuisine": "Kenyan",
  "diet": [
